            }
          ],
          "answer": "$p(x) = (x - 2)(2x^2 + x + 3)$",
          "solution": "Dividing $2x^3 - 3x^2 + x - 6$ by $(x - 2)$:$$p(x) = (x - 2)(2x^2 + x + 3).$$",
          "verify": [
