          "answer": "$|z| = 2$, $\\arg z = \\dfrac{\\pi}{3}$",
          "solution": "$$|z| = \\sqrt{1^2 + (\\sqrt{3})^2} = 2, \\qquad \\arg z = \\arctan\\sqrt{3} = \\frac{\\pi}{3}.$$",
